org.openimaj.rdf.owl2java

Class Generator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.rdf.owl2java.Generator

  • public class Generator
extends Object
    The main class of the OWL 2 Java tool. This class provides a main method that will convert an OWL/RDFS file to a set of Java code files that compile to provide an object representation of the ontology.
    Version:
    $Author$, $Revision$, $Date$
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk), David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
